From f5cb7a067d495589104715b8d215ea24878e9ae3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gemini PDA Mainline Project <noreply@example.com>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 08:52:32 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 35/36] dt-bindings: display: mediatek: add MT6797 fixed
 functions

MT6797 has COLOR, CCORR, AAL, GAMMA, OD, DITHER, and UFOE blocks in its
primary display pipeline. Their resource layouts and register generations
have been recovered independently from the retained source and running
Gemini state. Add dedicated compatibles for those blocks.

Signed-off-by: Gemini PDA Mainline Project <noreply@example.com>
